<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, October 6 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 1,923.95 on Tuesday, up 31.51
points, or 1.67 percent, from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was heavy with the turnover reaching over 44
trillion Turkish Liras (about 160 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went up 53.28 points, or 2.40 percent, to
close at 2,267.76 points, the industrial index rose 0.33 point to
close at 1,669.93 and the service index climbed 39.27 points, or
1.46 percent, to close at 1,932.75 points. 
</P>
</TEXT>
