President Moi, accompanied by his Ugandan counterpart Yoweri
Museveni, toured around the show ground before opening the trade
fair.
</P>
<P>
He was presented with a souvenir at the ceremony and UMA
donated 10,000 U.S. Dollars for the bereaved families of the
August 7 bombing in Nairobi.
</P>
<P>
UMA, established 10 years ago, held its first international
trade fair in 1993 and one in each year ever since. 
