<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 7 (Xinhua) -- The Ecuadorian soccer
federation has announced its national team roster for a friendly
match against Brazil on October 14 at RFK Stadium in Washington.
</P>
<P>
Among those chosen was 19-year-old forward Ivan Kaviedes, who
is considered one of the rising stars in South America.
</P>
<P>
