<HEADLINE> Stopping Chinese Army, Armed Police, and Government Businesses (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
He said that an arrangement has been made to carry out the
decision and that a thorough investigation should be made of the
situation and policies and programs worked out to provide a
foundation for further work.
</P>
<P>
If the corruption isn't dealt with systematically, the Party,
the State, and the military will be affected, he said, and the
socialist country destroyed, and that coordination, social and
political stability, strict discipline, and strengthened
leadership are needed for the work.
</P>
