</P>
<P>
The BSE-200 and U.S. dollar index were quoted up at 312.64 and
122.62 points compared with previous close of 303.80 and 119.29
respectively.
</P>
<P>
Equities on BSE market Wednesday made big gains as the Unit
Trust of India (UTI), the largest financial institution in India,
made aggressive purchases injecting confidence in the market.
</P>
<P>
A sharp rally in global markets, particularly Hong Kong and
Japan, also boosted the sentiment and even attracted some foreign
funds. 
</P>
</TEXT>
