</P>
<P>
-- Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji and his British counterpart Tony
Blair announced plans to establish a Sino-British comprehensive
partnership during their talks here yesterday.
</P>
<P>
The two sides have agreed that Chinese President Jiang Zemin
will pay a state visit to Britain in the latter half of 1999 at
