<P>
Jordan has strained relations with Syria, who has been blaming
the kingdom for staying too close with Israel.
</P>
<P>
Syria is now under pressure from Turkey, who earlier manifested
that it is in a state of undeclared war with Syria due to
Damascus' alleged support for the Kurdish rebels.
</P>
<P>
